aging error analysis

Source: R/age_error.R
age_error.Rd

aging error analysis

age_error(
  reader_tester = NULL,
  species,
  year,
  admb_home = NULL,
  area = "GOA",
  rec_age = 2,
  plus_age = 45,
  max_age = 100
)

Arguments

species

= "NORK"
year

= year of the assessment
admb_home

= location admb exists on your computer - if is "c:/admb" can leave NULL
area

= "GOA" (BSAI not currently setup)
rec_age

= recruitment age
plus_age

= max age for modeling
max_age

= max age for age error analysis - default = 100
read_tester

= if left blank it looks for the following file:"data/user_input/reader_tester.csv"

Value

Examples

ageage(species = "NORK", year = 2020, admb_home = NULL, area = "GOA", rec_age = 2, plus_age = 45, max_age = 100, ...)
